  "Storyline Chart": "Storyline Chart",
  "The xkcd movie-narrative idiom as an analytical chart. Every entity is a line that weaves between groups over time, so joins, departures and migrations read as movement. Org changes, team composition, customer-segment migration, coalition shifts. Crossings are minimized with a barycentre sweep.": "The xkcd movie-narrative idiom as an analytical chart. Every entity is a line that weaves between groups over time, so joins, departures and migrations read as movement. Org changes, team composition, customer-segment migration, coalition shifts. Crossings are minimized with a barycentre sweep.",
